<section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3px 7px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(232, 129, 241); border-top-left-radius: 6px; border-top-right-radius: 6px; border-bottom-right-radius: 6px; border-bottom-left-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; word-wrap: break-word !important;">0<span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">1</span></section><section style="margin: 6px 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">什么是禅修？</section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 3em; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(63, 63, 63); float: right; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section style="margin: 3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-wi