yle="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">禅宗强调“行住坐卧，无不是禅”的境界，就是告诉我们打坐只是禅修的一种形式。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">禅修的关键不在于是不是坐着，最重要的是知道坐在那里干什么。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果懂得了禅修的原理，打坐是禅修，就算是在吃饭、走路，甚至是在睡觉的时候也可以是禅修。</span></p><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 677px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 677px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dashed; border-left-color: rgb(83, 74, 71); background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(63, 62, 63); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">常见误区二：</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“禅修的目的是让头脑完全放空，什么想法都不能有。”</span></strong></p></section></section><section style="margin: -20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-bottom-width: 20px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-left-width: 20px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: transparent; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">首先，一般人做不到什么想法都没有，如果真的什么想法都没有，人就变成了石头、木头。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">其次，禅修的目的，不在于放空头脑，而是能够清楚觉察自己心里在想什么，并且对照智慧的文化，有意识的改变内心，尽可能的去除不良的品质，开显优秀的品质。</span></p><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 677px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 677px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dashed; border-left-color: rgb(83, 74, 71); background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(63, 62, 63); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">常见误区三：</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“只要有一个安静的环境，坚持坐在那里就能获得平静的心。”</span></strong></p></section></section><section style="margin: -20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-bottom-width: 20px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-left-width: 20px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: transparent; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">获得内心的完全平静是禅修最终所能达到的状态，也就是佛陀涅槃寂静的状态。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">但达到完全的平静需要一个漫长的过程，而且也不是靠一动不动的坐在那里就能达到的。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">最重要的是懂得正确用心的方法，否则一直坐着也没有什么帮助。如果方法对了，内心有一分改变，就会有一分收获，有立竿见影的效果。</span></p><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 677px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 677px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dashed; border-left-color: rgb(83, 74, 71); background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(63, 62, 63); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">常见误区四：</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“打坐很危险，不小心就会走火入魔。”</span></strong></p></section></section><section style="margin: -20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-bottom-width: 20px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-left-width: 20px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: transparent; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这是在开始进入禅定状态之后需要担心的事情，对于大多数零基础的人来说，距离这个境界还远，完全可以采用没有副作用的方法进行禅修体验。</span></p><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px auto -8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 20px; height: 25px; background-color: rgb(252, 217, 239); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(136, 139, 138); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(97, 97, 97); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这门课程就是提供了一种专为现代人设计的轻禅修方法，让零基础的人足不出户就能体验到禅修的好处。</strong></p></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3px 7px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; background-color: rgb(232, 129, 241); border-top-left-radius: 6px; border-top-right-radius: 6px; border-bottom-right-radius: 6px; border-bottom-left-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; word-wrap: break-word !important;">0<span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">3</span></section><section style="margin: 6px 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">如何体验线上“轻禅修”</section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 3em; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(63, 63, 63); float: right; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section style="margin: 3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; width: 169.734375px; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(63, 63, 63); float: right; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">线上轻禅修步骤一：看佛陀故事</span></strong><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">通过观看视频了解佛陀一生的故事，通过这位圣者的视角重新看待世界、看待人生。</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这部分学习就是利用我们的</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">理性思维</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">，思考自己看待人生的方式与佛陀有哪些差异。</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">一方面思考自己原有观念的局限，以及这种局限会带来哪些坏处；另一方面思考佛陀智慧的独到之处，以及这种智慧会带来哪些好处，思考自己是否需要改变。</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果能用佛陀的智慧指导人生，就完成了一次禅修。</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">线上轻禅修步骤二：亲自参与绘画</span></strong><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">仅有知识层面的学习还是不够的，通过实践才能把字面知识转变成自己的东西。</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">现代人生活在信息碎片化的网络时代，已经很难安静的坐下来了。所以我们提供的是一种生动有趣，具有美感的实践方式——绘画。</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">专注于绘画的过程有助于提高觉知力，在学习绘画时一旦走神，就会在画面中有所体现。</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">觉知力是能让你觉察到自己在做什么的能力。</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果缺乏觉知力，内心就容易陷入到各种混乱的负面情绪中，甚至完全无法控制自己。</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果具有觉知力，就能够更好的投入到当下的生活中，不因过去遗憾，也不为未来过分担忧，自然提升幸福感。</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在绘画中培养觉知力，并将这种能力带入到生活的每个场景，逐渐就能体验到“行住坐卧无不是禅”的境界。</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">线上轻禅修步骤三：回顾佛陀智慧</span></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">我们画的每一幅画都来源于佛陀故事的一个片段，直观的画面可以增强你的</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">想象力。</span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">帮助你轻松的回到故事中去，再一次回顾佛陀的智慧，感受佛陀视角下清净无染的世界。</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">同时借助画面的美感，内心逐渐从混乱状态变得平静，达到消除烦恼，舒缓压力的效果。</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(112, 48, 160); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">通过这三个步骤，你的理性思维、觉知力和想象力得到提升，你的心就因此得到训练，而这就是禅修最核心的意义所在。</span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">为什么一定要选择佛陀传作为“轻禅修”的一部分？</span></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px 5px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 等线; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">佛教有别与西方哲学，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">西方哲学更多带人们探讨问题，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">没有结果也没有方法，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">佛教则是帮助人们看到问题并找到方法，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 等线; font-size: 15px; 